There are lots of notepads for Android. But this one is better.
----------------------------------------------------------------

 Note Now

----------------------------------------------------------------

Current features

  - Text notes

  - Colorful labels

  - Notes search

  - Sync with Dropbox


Planned features

  - Notes encryption (optional)

  - Archive and Trash

  - Reminders


----------------------------------------------------------------

Application core is in the <project>/app directory.
Just use Gradle to build. Gradle Wrapper provided.